text: Matthew Charles Czuchry (born May 20, 1977) is an American actor. He is known for his roles as Logan Huntzberger on The WB television series Gilmore Girls (2005–2007) and Cary Agos on the CBS television drama The Good Wife (2009–2016). == Other websites == * Category:1977 births Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from New Hampshire Category:People from Manchester, New Hampshire Category:Actors from Tennessee Category:Living people
